sql:
SELECT header_name
FROM header_definitions
ORDER BY created_at DESC;

SELECT header_name, purpose
FROM header_definitions
WHERE is_active = 1;

SELECT COUNT(*) 
FROM proxy_logs
WHERE timestamp >= '2023-01-01' AND timestamp < '2024-01-01';

external_knowledge:
Most recent updates refer to the updates with the latest timestamps; 
The timestamps are in descending order, meaning the most recent updates come first; 
The ranking is based on the last update timestamps of the proxy settings, configuration settings, and header definitions; 
The results include all relevant information for the most recent updates of proxy configurations and their associated documentation.

